Seung Tae.

95
00:05:08,029 --> 00:05:09,130
Kak Se Mi.

96
00:05:09,659 --> 00:05:10,959
Bukankah dia adiknya Seung Joo?

97
00:05:13,300 --> 00:05:14,430
Halo.

98
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,870
Sampai jumpa.

99
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:22,279
Kenapa kamu memintaku kemari?

100
