- Kami sudah berpacaran.

120
00:06:04,579 --> 00:06:05,690
Jeong Mi.

121
00:06:06,719 --> 00:06:07,750
Kamu berpacaran dengannya?

122
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:08,760
