168
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,860
Astaga.

169
00:07:56,260 --> 00:07:58,229
Kenapa rasa kopinya begini?

170
00:07:58,469 --> 00:08:00,329
Kakak memakai biji kopi murah?

171
